  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb2\u0bcb\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gamini Senarath becomes Ranil's advisor",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is learned that former Presidential Secretary Kamini Senarath will be appointed as an advisor to President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Kamini Senarath served as Presidential Secretary during the tenure of Ranil Wickremesinghe as Acting President and during the tenure of former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "Following Ranil Wickremesinghe's inauguration as the 8th Executive President and the appointment of Saman Ekanayake as his secretary, it is understood that the President has decided to appoint Kamini Senarat, a 35-year civil service officer, as an advisor.",
        "It is noteworthy that Kamini Senarath has a long experience of serving as President's Secretary and Prime Minister's Secretary."
      ],
